Package: cowprompt
Architecture: all
Depends: xcowsay, fortune-mod, ${misc:Depends}
Description: CowPrompt is a wrapper for xcowsay and fortune to display prompts.
 CowPrompt is a simple wrapper program for xcowsay and fortune that can be used to display any message contained in a fortune data file to the screen.
 The main intent for CowPrompt is to display writing prompts for writers taking part in self-challenges, but can be used for any purpose where prompts need to be displayed onto the screen on demand.
